Package it.polito.verifoo.rest.common

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddressMapping
    This class generate the Address Mapping List between nodename and nodeip.
    Link
    This class is being used to convert the neighbor node notion into a more convenient form in order to pass the correct information to Verifoo
    LogReader
    This class implements a way to retrive the log with a limited number of lines
    NetContextGenerator
    This class generate the nework context (the link between nodenames and node ip in z3)
    NodeNetworkObject
    This class generates a Map of a new network object and associated node.
    PacketWrapper
    This class convert our EndHost Packet Model configuration in the verigraph one
    Translator
    This class implements a parser for verifoo output for find on witch host verifoo deploy a node
    VerifooProxy
    This is the main class that will interface with the Verifoo classes
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadGraphError
    This class represents the main exception that will be thrown by the VerifooProxy Class
